                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Sir,</p>\n\t\t\t<p rend=\"indent(2)\">Your Draft of contract dated <date>20<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi></date>\n\t\t\t\tInst.<lb/> left with me not being on the terms prescribed<lb/> by the congregation.\n\t\t\t\tI herewith return you the<lb/> same. Hoping you will still execute the one<lb/> left\n\t\t\t\twith you.<lb/></p>\n\t\t\t<p rend=\"indent(10)\">Yours respectfully</p>\n\t\t\t<p rend=\"indent(10)\">\n\t\t\t\t<persName role=\"author\">Lewis Allen</persName>\n\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t<p rend=\"indent(11)\">Parnass</p>\n\t\t\t<p rend=\"indent(11)\">K. K. M. Israel</p>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t<date>25/37 Decbr.</date>\n\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t<p><date>Sunday</date> morning</p>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t<addressee>Revd Mr I. Leeser</addressee>\n\t\t\t</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3dr2pv8d/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
